            {
               "text": "<h3>Subcontinent: North America</h3>In this map, the subcontinent North America (<i>Abya Yala</i>) is highlighted, while the regions of South America (<i>Abya Yala</i>), Asia, and Europe are also represented. It is important to note that Central America (<i>Abya Yala</i>) and North America (<i>Abya Yala</i>) are presented as a unified subcontinent; however, some studies treat them separately",
